name: Yopmail Signature Flow - Safe DocuSign Flow

Fill vendor questions and click Add Signature
Click getByRole('button', { name: 'Add Signature in AOL PDF' })
Is visible locator('span').filter({ hasText: 'I agree to use electronic' }).first()
